{"tid":2280464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fact check你個fact check　話200歲選民係fake其實係fake","createTime":"2020-11-10T13:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T13:57:44.000Z","uid":261647,"like":136,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9c952c4e042e9b6e4b0601f5eda6d5d12548a400","tid":2280464,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/osreadhistory/photos/a.299410663590132/1442660365931817/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fosreadhistory%2Fphotos%2Fa.299410663590132%2F1442660365931817%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=f66edbc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/osreadhistory/photos/a.299410663590132/1442660365931817/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n最近有流傳一批圖，指美國人公民即使到200歲都仍然盡力盡好公民責任<br />\n即刻有fact check話200歲選民係fake，因為依賓州法律，所有私隱需要特別保護既人，例如家暴受害者，佢地既出生日期都會係固定既1800年1月1日，然後就據此證實全部都係fake<br />\n<br />\n好<br />\n示範一下正確既fact check方法俾大家睇<br />\n<br />\n首先第一件事要質疑既，係資料來源是否正確<br />\n呢方面政府係唯一真確既資料來源，所以要搵返個資料庫網站出黎<br />\n結果查到呢個網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://data.pa.gov/Government-Efficiency-Citizen-Engagement/2020-General-Election-Mail-Ballot-Requests-Departm/mcba-yywm/data\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.pa.gov%2FGovernment-Efficiency-Citizen-Engagement%2F2020-General-Election-Mail-Ballot-Requests-Departm%2Fmcba-yywm%2Fdata&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=874b5e34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://data.pa.gov/Government-Efficiency-Citizen-Engagement/2020-General-Election-Mail-Ballot-Requests-Departm/mcba-yywm/data</a><br />\n確定係屬於賓州政府所有，所以亦知道郵遞選民數據係賓州一州既數據<br />\n<br />\n其次要質疑既，係數字準唔準確<br />\n咁最簡單既方法就係自己計一次<br />\n由於1800年1月1日出生既人都係假出生日期，所以要先排除佢地<br />\n呢度係57筆資料<br />\n<br />\n然後我要訂一個合理既統計年限<br />\n雖然有人會有100歲命，但以2020年10月31日當日滿100歲作統計下限可以包括到最多可能性<br />\n<br />\n由於1800年1月1日係假出生日期，為求保險，通常係做考證時會將所有類似既情況分開列出，以免有漏網<br />\n所以我就用人手將1920年10月31日以前於1月1日出生既所有人統計出黎，並排除於所有統計以外<br />\n分別係<br />\n1800年：57筆<br />\n1900年：18筆<br />\n1901年：4筆<br />\n1919年：1筆<br />\n1920年：6筆<br />\n都86筆<br />\n<br />\n可以見到1900年人數係多得非常可疑，而且都120歲，年齡亦非常可疑<br />\n反正我就假設係人為因素全部排除<br />\n重要既事講三次，所有1月1日出生既數據，全部無條件排除，全部無條件排除，全部無條件排除<br />\n<br />\n咁一共有幾多個人瑞以郵遞方式投左票呢？<br />\n一共係1459筆資料<br />\n<br />\n跟住下一步，就係分析數據<br />\n因為我其實都好多野做，多野做到連乃木戀既男朋友活動都唔得閒玩<br />\n所以我只做一個最簡單快捷亦好能說明問題既分析<br />\n就係各年齡既人口分佈<br />\n<br />\n排除所有生於1月1日既選票之後，一共有1459筆資料係投票日前介於100歲至220歲之間<br />\n<br />\n當中200歲至220歲既選民有1人<br />\n150歲至199歲既選民有2人<br />\n120歲至149歲既選民有15人<br />\n110歲至119歲既選民有15人<br />\n100歲至109歲既選民有1426人<br />\n<br />\n109歲，2人<br />\n108歲，7人<br />\n107歲，12人<br />\n106歲，22人<br />\n105歲，36人<br />\n104歲，71人<br />\n103歲，114人<br />\n102歲，217人<br />\n101歲，316人<br />\n100歲，629人<br />\n以上數字無條件排除所有1月1日出生既任何人<br />\n<br />\n要留意返啦，呢個數因為用人手數，所以難免眼昏腦脹有錯<br />\n有興趣既不妨自己將數據放入電腦用電腦數一次<br />\n而且真係要查證，其實仲可以比對州既人口資料<br />\n例如各年齡同州既人口年齡分佈既關係<br />\n投票意向仲有寄出地址等等，好多交叉分析可以做<br />\n<br />\n我單純想fc下人地既fc<br />\n<br />\n所以呢<br />\n上網抄fc唔係fc囉<br />\n人地話自己fc左你就信架啦<br />\n<br />\n咁今日ABC都projected蔡英文係泰國總統啦<br />\nfc，係專業黎既<br />\n我就返去照顧下我個虛擬女朋友啦，係咁多<br />\n#hooky<br />\n<br />\nps：其實資料庫入面有至少202筆資料係無出世年齡，因為我部電腦只讀到一百萬筆資料，有2,098,705筆資料無法讀取，所以數量應該只會多唔會少<br />\n至於人瑞人口就係係網站上面數，應該無問題<br />\n猜測，無出生日期既選票應該係官方未檢查既選票，所以官方覺得有220歲既選民係好合理，well，官僚嘛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bg0OodG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBg0OodG.png&h=a8d6cc10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31c221d45fd809be652a293e79b963dcf603ba9b","tid":2280464,"uid":198595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"推講得好"},{"pid":"da1c936063338357b73547b1fdb6d7b5d86344b8","tid":2280464,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"Exposed"},{"pid":"3ab0f303879b392c12bbb38d81358f34e61b75b0","tid":2280464,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"我建議蘋果同立場派妓者去陰間FACT CHECK"},{"pid":"d3b6ebfc859bf9efbeb33f56053c271f2afad91b","tid":2280464,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e40cdf96e3df6f3901d899151b9865d82326c3b","tid":2280464,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c89fd4d0ef0b90d137e573c85606c5b4c1bfc15c","tid":2280464,"uid":47222,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:25:25.000Z","msg":"PR慣常招數 搬單一fake news出黎講到所有都係fake"},{"pid":"1fc3aeaedb33d340d7718d3772351a5b13dcfa76","tid":2280464,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328d1bcee6292ed2f968917e9d8442156493bcbd","tid":2280464,"uid":70818,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\nbtw 多野做到連乃木戀既男朋友活動都唔得閒玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n辛苦巴打了"},{"pid":"4b73d89be52d052a78a52ddef7a58b620781de0a","tid":2280464,"uid":38566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src